name: KINGS' SOLE
description:
First published novel from Mark Hamilton aka. Notorious Coo
Product Description
"Kings' Sole is the uplifting story of one man's desire to conceal his true life and identity to appease the one he loves. Kenny, a native Los Angelino, has climbed up the ladder to create a regional drug empire. As the west coast primary distributor, Kenny and his crew are living large. Although everything on the surface seems fine with Kenny having ties to not only the Mexican Mafia but also the leaders and Gangsters of the major Los Angeles neighborhood sets, he quickly learns that once love enters the picture it becomes more than a minor complication, as well as the fact that good things don't tend to last forever.

Sole is a down home sweetheart, with a heart big as the ocean, she only wishes to help any and everyone she can. Losing her mother and father to drugs, Sole has developed a passionate dislike for the chemicals as well as their progenitors. Finding love is the last thing on Sole,s mind but when she meets Kenny, a smooth gently soul, she feels that she can finally let go and lose herself in his warm embrace.

Oblivious to Kenny's true identity, Sole allows herself to fall for Kenny in ways she has never before fallen for a man. Their connection is just too great and seems to be able to withstand anything, or can it?"
